brewery.brewery_description:
CRAFT BEER IS NOT A CRIME
Handcrafted Beer from Germany

CREW Republic stands for honest, craft-brewed beers of extraordinary flavor. We are constantly on the lookout for the best hop varieties in the world and creating new recipes. A refuge for all those who aren’t satisfied with the “standardized beers”.

We brew what we like and we only bottle what‘s perfect. Yes, that means we break with tradition and, no, we aren’t always popular. Our beer isn´t for everybody. There‘s enough run-of-the-mill as it is.

Our beers are found only in select bars and restaurants. No matter where you live, our web shop will deliver the revolution for more flavor and variety in the German beer world directly to your front door with no shipping cost!

JOIN THE REVOLUTION!

beer.beer_description:
Weigh the Anchor, Hoist the Sails! Colossal waves and lashing winds – this was the life of the English sailors who had to bring the beer to Colonial India. Only with an insane amount of hops and high alcohol content could it withstand the perilous journey. Drunken Sailor IPA brings this adventure and powerful taste to the 21st century – Ship Ahoy!

Classic IPA with exotic hop aromas.

Full-bodied & Hop Aromatic. A voyage of intense yet rounded aromas of tropical fruits and citrus

Hops: Herkules, Citra, Cascade, Simcoe
Malt: Pilsener, Munich, Crystal

Hops: Galaxy, Mosaic, Amarillo, Citra

Malts: Pilsner, wheat, oat, caramel malt

7:45 AM. Your friends have all gone home and the barkeeper is kicking you out because you’re the last one at the bar... again. But you just won’t stop partying! We dedicate this beer to you – always the last one standing long after we have all fallen into our beds. You are the hero of the night!

Hops: Columbus, Simcoe, Amarillo, Chinook
Malt: Pilsener, Munich, Crystal

Hops are your surfboard, the Sunshine State your synonym for paradise. In Your Face gives you that West Coast feeling. Ferocious waves slam into your face. It's too much for everyone else, but you're just getting started. You're not afraid of the great white shark. You yearn for this brutal punch of hops. Shaka!

Light, dry, and aggressively hoppy:
California in a glass.

Dry & Aggressive. Citrus, exotic fruits, fresh pine resin, and uncompromising bitterness.

Hops: Centennial, Chinook, Simcoe, Citra, Herkules
Malt: Pilsener, Munich, Crystal

2011, somewhere in a small apartment in Munich. Two aficionados with their first new homebrew kit are experimenting with malt and hop varieties from across the globe. Their goal: A beer that will revolutionize the world of German beer. Foundation 11 was the foundation stone for CREW Republic and the German Craft Beer Revolution.

Hops: Tradition, Mosaic, Citra, Cascade
Malt: Pilsener, Munich, Crystal

A quiet evening in front of the fireplace: Crackling wood, dancing flames – 
and then a kick straight to the face! Roundhouse Kick Imperial Stout! Brewed for those whose taste buds can never get enough! A real malt and hop bomb – black as night and explosive as dynamite!

Hops: Columbus, Tradition
Malt: Pilsener, Chocolate, Crystal, Roasted

Grilling by the Isar River, relaxing with friends, soaking up the sun in the mountains – that is summer at CREW Republic and our Easy is the beer to go with it! Positively hoppy and refreshing. This is our tribute to the most beautiful time of the year at the most beautiful place on earth!

Hops: Tradition, Citra, Cascade, Comet, Amarillo
Malt: Pilsener, Munich, Crystal

You’ve still got so much to do, or maybe once again you've already done your fair share. You’ve been jonesin’ for it all day long. From the moment you woke you could think of nothing else… Here is your own personal hop fix – you’re welcome!

Hops: Comet, Galaxy, Chinook
Malt: Pilsener, Munich, Crystal

Du liebst die Tradition, lebst aber nicht in der Vergangenheit. Du gehst neue Wege, vergisst aber niemals Deine Wurzeln. Du willst die Welt erobern, aber Deine Heimat ist Dir heilig. Du bist unser Local Hero! Bleib wie Du bist.

Frisches Helles mit besonderem. Twist durch die späte Gabe traditioneller Hopfensorten. Viel Aroma ohne Bittere!

Strohgelb, weich und rund. Ein milder Körper mit einzigartigem dezentem Hopfenaroma, das an Limette erinnert.

Hopfen: Tradition, Hersbrucker
Malz: Pilsener, Karamellmalz

There's no question that you are excessive. You greet the resentment of others with steady ignorance. You meet accusations of overconfi dence with cool arrogance. You live out your lust for life in gluttony. This elixir is made for you. The beginning and end of your dreams.

Hops: Herkules, Fuggles, East Kent Golding
Malt: Pilsener, Crystal

- eXperimental line - 

It is way past midnight. Pitch black. Only a small brewery is burning the midnight oil. The CREW has gathered to experiment. No new hop, no idea for a recipe will be spared – however only the best will make it into the bottle. Beers with on the label have been brewed by us for the first time and no one knows if they will ever be brewed again…

An evening at the bar together with old friends: Stories from the past, memories of shared adventures. A carefree time. Like a long night by the fire accompanied by the soft crackling of the wood and the flickering light of the flames. May the evening never end...

A varied blend of specialty malts gives a velvety maltiness that is not overbearing but is rich in colour.

Bright red colour with a pleasantly full, yet not too heavy body. Slightly fruity-malty taste.

Hops: Tradition, Fuggles, East Kent Golding

Malt: Pilsner, melanoidin, caramel, roasted malt

Brewmaster’s Notes
Eine Hopfenbombe. Orange, trüb und saftig-fruchtig. 

Tasting
Eine Explosion tropischer Früchte im Geruch. Ein Fruchtcocktail im Geschmack mit verhaltener Bittere und leichter Süße. Hoppy and Juicy!

Food Pairing
Die CREW genießt ihr NEW England IPA am liebsten zu gereiftem Hartkäse oder leichtem Seafood.
